irects, and streaming. Avoid OAuth2-specific coverage unless adding `io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2:5.0.1`, because `OAuth2WebClient` depends on that optional artifact.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The native-run workaround is inferred from the resolved 5.0.1 dependency tree pulling Netty 4.2.2.Final and from the existing 5.0.0 build logic; local Gradle/native-image verification remains authoritative.\",\n    \"Testing OAuth2WebClient without the optional `vertx-auth-oauth2` dependency can cause compilation or runtime linkage issues, but OAuth2 is not required for baseline meaningful WebClient coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_003c6df87da38334016a4136d5d4e081959b4c62811b081b06\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1173, "output": 861, "cacheRead": 31232, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33266, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782658762973, "responseId": "resp_003c6df87da38334016a4136cbf9808195a2af8b4373a745f3"}}
